    ViewData["Title"] = "About Me";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Aurora Brickwell's World</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #666;
        }
        .signature {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #999;
            text-align: right;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Aurora Brickwell's World</h1>
        <p>Aurora Brickwell isn't just any Lego™ enthusiast; she's a renowned collector and a master builder, celebrated for her unparalleled passion for Lego sets and her exceptional talent in crafting unique designs. With a large social media following, Aurora has captured the hearts of Lego fans worldwide, captivating them with her stunning creations and sharing her expertise with fellow enthusiasts.</p>
        <p>Aurora's journey into the world of Lego began in her childhood, where she discovered the joy of building with these iconic bricks. Over the years, her love for Lego only grew stronger, fueling her desire to explore new possibilities and push the boundaries of what's possible with these timeless toys. As she honed her skills and developed her own distinct style, Aurora's reputation as a Lego aficionado continued to soar, earning her recognition within the community and beyond.</p>
        <p>Driven by her passion and creativity, Aurora embarked on a mission to share her love for Lego with the world. Leveraging her distributor license with The Lego Group™, she turned her hobby into a thriving business, using her social media platforms to showcase her collection, offer exclusive sets, and connect with fellow Lego enthusiasts. Through her dedication and unwavering commitment, Aurora has built a loyal following of fans who eagerly anticipate her next masterpiece.</p>
        <p>As Aurora's business continues to flourish, she recognizes the need to evolve and expand her reach. With a vision to create a seamless shopping experience for her customers, Aurora has decided to launch her own web app-based storefront. Partnering with a consulting firm, she aims to transition her sales from social media channels to her website while offering her customers a convenient platform to explore her curated collection of Lego sets and purchase her unique designs.</p>
        <p>Aurora's website will not only feature her extensive range of Lego products but also serve as a hub for creativity and inspiration, showcasing her latest creations, offering design tips, and fostering a vibrant community of Lego enthusiasts. With a focus on user experience and innovation, Aurora is excited to embark on this new chapter, inviting fans old and new to join her on a journey fueled by imagination and endless possibilities.</p>
        <p>Join Aurora Brickwell on her quest to build a world of endless creativity, brick by brick!</p>
        <p class="signature">Thank you</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
